songs.title: Interlude
songs.album: CitizensFOB Mixtape: Welcome to the New Administration
songs.lyrics:
What up, this is Ludacris. Letting you know the new Fall Out Boy album in stores November 4th

New album is called Folie à Deux, or Folie à Deux, man I don’t know how to, man I don’t speak French! What the fuck is this?

Pete man, I see you trying to DJ right? Now I hear you wanna be a rapper? Man, don’t even, don’t even try come into my territory man

I’ll battle you to the death

Yo Clinton Sparks, do what you do best, and get these people familiar, god damnit
Get familiar
Why the fuck would y'all name your album some shit people can’t even pronounce? This some bullshit!

Just make sure you go get it when it come out

Luda! Haha!
